        "text": "and wound it in linen clothes ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Wrapped it in a great many folds of linen; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "with the spices, as the manner of the Jews is to bury ",
        "children": []
