        "text": "cloths",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The ‘cloths’ seem to refer to the bandages which kept the whole together rather than the large ‘linen sheet’ mentioned by the other Evangelists, which Joseph had bought on purpose (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
